# PURPOSE: Optimize Docker build performance and security by excluding 
#          unnecessary files, secrets, and local development artifacts. 
# ==============================================================================

# ðŸŽ© MadHatter Summary:
# ---------------------
# - The Sentry (White Hat): Ensures sensitive .env files stay on the host, 
#   preventing secrets from being baked into the image layers.
# - The Ghost (Green Hat): Strips away local Git history and IDE metadata, 
#   making the final container image as light as possible.
# - The Professor (Blue Hat): A lesson in "Build Context" optimizationâ€”only 
#   send the code actually needed to run the service.
# - The Janitor (Red Hat): Sweeps up Windows "garbage" like Thumbs.db and 
#   temp files that cause clutter in Linux-based containers.

# ==============================================================================
# Secrets & Environment (CRITICAL)
# ==============================================================================
# Prevent embedding secrets in the image layers. 
# Compose will still inject these at runtime via `env_file`.
.env
.env.*
*.env
.old
secrets/
certs/
*.pem
*.key

# ==============================================================================
# Version Control & IDEs
# ==============================================================================
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.dockerignore
.vscode/
.vs/
*.code-workspace
.idea/
*.suo
*.user

# ==============================================================================
# Local Data & Volumes
# ==============================================================================
# Exclude folders where containers store their persistent data
**/data/
**/db_data/
**/postgres_data/
**/redis_data/
**/logs/
**/npm/
**/pihole/

# ==============================================================================
# Build Artifacts & Dependencies
# ==============================================================================
node_modules/
npm-debug.log
obj/
bin/
dist/
*.log

# ==============================================================================
# OS Specific (Windows Junk)
# ==============================================================================
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/